{"tid":726307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"轉發帖文歌頌中國是「最大贏家」　台灣歌手溫嵐捱轟","createTime":"2018-07-02T09:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T16:47:03.000Z","uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c888764c9fac512acdfe726e7d79d9e80da61646","tid":726307,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:32:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00004/1530522100298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00004%2F1530522100298&d=wJQDztqai%2BickeFlznggjUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=eea0b9e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00004%2F1530522100298&h=61de1404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00004/1530522100298</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然中國國家隊無緣參與世界盃分組賽事，不少中國人仍然為國家在不同程度參與世界盃感到光榮。曾與亞洲天王周杰倫多次合作的台灣歌手溫嵐，日前在FB發文，指出「這屆世界盃，最大的贏家是中國」。<br />\n<br />\n溫嵐指，中國隊雖然沒有參加，但是世界盃完全被中國人壟斷，「世界盃開幕式出現了6名中國旗手」、「世界盃比賽用球全部是中國廣東東莞生產」、「世界盃的賽場廣告，被中國萬達公司、蒙牛公司、海信、中國ViVo公司基本壟斷」、「中國人一共買了4萬3千張門票」、「中國有12萬球迷到俄羅斯觀賽」。<br />\n<br />\n溫嵐列明，帖文是轉載自好友，全篇以簡體字書寫，內容不斷歌頌中國的偉大。不少網民仍然批評溫嵐過分渲染，認為她背棄中華民國。<br />\n<br />\n有一個留言曰：「這種發文還是去微博發發吧。」獲得讚好數目，比溫嵐原帖所得還要多。亦有眼利網民質疑，為什麼12萬人到俄羅斯，但只買了4萬3千張門票：「總不可能搭機去俄羅斯看電視轉播吧？」<br />\n<br />\n社運人士王奕凱亦在FB指出，溫嵐文章只是轉發，屬世界盃開始內地網絡開始流傳的嘲諷文。溫嵐之後亦再出帖，請網友學會欣賞：「學會欣賞，就能發現世界上的美好，生活將會為之明朗。懂得欣賞，就能體會每個人的辛苦不易，工作起來也將更為和諧進步。」有中國網友留言表示支持，反斥罵溫嵐的人沒有言論自由、「台獨分子」。<br />\n<br />\n溫嵐已刪去世足「中國之最」一文。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180702/s00004/86275d720a6796a67aaed9060c966b9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180702%2Fs00004%2F86275d720a6796a67aaed9060c966b9d.jpg&h=257e9120&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d3befdab94b9e8f4e7d38cd53e1a16330667509","tid":726307,"uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"曲線？真心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6292e1c5851cfb902b01076fb83fdf55afb21a4","tid":726307,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c205b85d1c637f3a6c32e3c74cae812ee50173eb","tid":726307,"uid":5489,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:13:36.000Z","msg":"咁撚曲麵俾台狗鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48437ad9f5402cc5cdc34844af7195009bf9af0","tid":726307,"uid":38540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"中國又贏"},{"pid":"4ebc9e88c7920af8ddb36b09802bc4d549aa5d12","tid":726307,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d3befdab94b9e8f4e7d38cd53e1a16330667509","tid":726307,"uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"曲線？真心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T18:21:26.000Z","msg":"唔知"},{"pid":"162a81ef4dc3da98f16f41027ae7e38cc23c3bfb","tid":726307,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T18:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 「中國人一共買了4萬3千張門票」、「中國有12萬球迷到俄羅斯觀賽」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剩餘果啲係買左假飛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99bf01f85b9b6e679587875eb9e21c40b3c3c81","tid":726307,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"162a81ef4dc3da98f16f41027ae7e38cc23c3bfb","tid":726307,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T18:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 「中國人一共買了4萬3千張門票」、「中國有12萬球迷到俄羅斯觀賽」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剩餘果啲係買左假飛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:14:00.000Z","msg":"獅子老虎籠都照翻牆入，老子會怕你幾個北極熊保